data.description: Many upgrades throughout this home!  Luxury vinyl plank flooring, gas range w/ double oven, Bosch dishwasher, pull out kitchen shelves, reverse osmosis water softener, central vac, built-in custom entertainment center, surround sound. Two attic fans on temp sensors. New roof 2017, Newer water heater, skylight, ceiling fans. Primary En Suite bathroom is an oasis w/ large custom shower, LED touch fog control mirrors, bluetooth enabled fan and Double vanities. Storage shed & RV Parking1 Large garage w/ built-in shelves. Gorgeous mature landscaping w/ pond/waterfall, 2 patios (15'x13'  28'x20'). garden area and more! Quiet neighborhood in the heart of Meridian w/ quick freeway access.
